{"tid":1218952,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"集思廣益：聽講TVB係主流媒體，如果TVB拍唔到嘢會點？","createTime":"2019-06-13T17:14:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T17:51:22.000Z","uid":206523,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f474d5854eb4c18e75b65df87a7dc1de7e6cdcde","tid":1218952,"uid":206523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:14:20.000Z","msg":"TVB傳播訊息真係好重要！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除咗有時市民唔覺意係TVB記者身邊不繼重覆咁大聲講出咗自己心底話（例如無線新聞是是但但）<br />\n仲有咩可能性會我睇唔到TVB？<br />\n利申：好想日日睇TVB讚林鄭，求下你哋唔好令我睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc187e3a5ab3b1d082d4df8ac6a892dcec3d3207","tid":1218952,"uid":131696,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:18:07.000Z","msg":"佢地好撚多記者 未必搞得晒<br />\n如果搞佢地 cam對住示威者搞事 會俾好大個位人入<br />\n搞記者後果同黑警一樣"},{"pid":"1d0e9bae9ea9b12a8714fbbf657bc25cee0203cb","tid":1218952,"uid":148987,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:44:15.000Z","msg":"V煞都有佔電視台"},{"pid":"04f9f8374b2dc6660298e69c6a78e1c58c1205e1","tid":1218952,"uid":15835,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:46:31.000Z","msg":"我 Respect 攝影師既<br />\n不過剪片果個就控制唔到啦"},{"pid":"da399eb62db63ccdac18e48f4fb12e850b6c588e","tid":1218952,"uid":35930,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:51:22.000Z","msg":"剪片果個應該係最高人工<br />\n<br />\n導演 編劇都撈埋 剪到顛倒是非黑白"}]}